description: Demolition of existing multi-storey car park and healthcare building and erection of part 5/part 6 storey building for a mixed use development comprising a two-level retail store (Class A1), 73 residential units (Class C3) and non-residential institutional use (Class D1); together with 928 (approx) car parking spaces (including basement parking) servicing area and formation of new vehicular accesses to Station Road and Augustus Lane and landscaping and other related works. (revision to scheme permitted under ref 04/03193 to include additional retail floor space on the mezzanine level and associated alterations) (Revised drawings received including elevational/layout alterations and reduction in mezzanine level to 50% cover plus additional statements received including revised Transport Assessment, supplementary Town Centre and Retail Statement and Access, Playspace and Energy Statements.)
